Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:08.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,スターサイドホテル
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.20,0:01:07.11,default,,0,0,0,,Starside Hotel...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.56,0:01:11.90,default,,0,0,0,,The bridge is 74m above ground.\NAnd they have to cross it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.59,0:01:11.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地上７４メートルの鉄骨渡り
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.04,0:01:15.82,default,,0,0,0,,The wind, the wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:16.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,風が… 風が！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.37,0:01:20.94,default,,0,0,0,,The final challenge where\Ntheir life's at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.39,0:01:21.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最終戦は命をかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.39,0:01:21.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ブレイブ・メン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.27,0:01:25.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勇者たちが進む２５メートル
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.37,0:01:24.44,default,,0,0,0,,The 25 meters gap that the\Nbrave men have to cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.54,0:01:27.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,太田！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:27.40,default,,0,0,0,,Oota!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.00,0:01:38.57,default,,0,0,0,,One down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.08,0:01:39.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.98,0:01:43.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう… 嫌だ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:42.16,default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:45.31,default,,0,0,0,,This bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.49,0:01:46.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな橋！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.56,0:01:48.32,default,,0,0,0,,- No! No!\N- Stop! Calm down, Akikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.22,0:01:48.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よせ 落ち着くんだ 秋川
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:02:01.53,default,,0,0,0,,Help me!\NSomeone! Please, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:02:01.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,助けてくれ 誰か助けてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.67,0:02:05.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ち着け 落ち着くんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:05.37,default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!\NPull yourselves together!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:08.61,kaiji-main-top,,0,0,0,,Dying Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:10.81,default,,0,0,0,,Help! Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:12.64,default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:14.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ち着け みんな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:16.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すみませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.28,0:02:19.38,default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. It's all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:20.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全部 俺が悪かった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:25.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きっと心を入れ替えますから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:25.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺を救ってください
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.13,0:02:22.78,default,,0,0,0,,I swear I'll change after this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:25.62,default,,0,0,0,,So, please save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:30.62,default,,0,0,0,,Make me stop trembling!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:30.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この体の震えを… 止めて！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:45.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:45.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ち着け 止まる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.19,0:02:43.37,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.37,0:02:44.48,default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.48,0:02:47.97,default,,0,0,0,,It'll stop. Relax, it'll stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:50.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少しこらえれば止まる 嵐は去る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.46,0:02:52.44,default,,0,0,0,,The storm will pass!\NUntil then, bear with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:52.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それまで頑張れ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:02:59.82,default,,0,0,0,,Nakayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:03:04.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中山 落ち着け
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:03.36,default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.42,0:03:07.83,default,,0,0,0,,Why?\NWhy did it come to this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:08.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何で… 何でこんなことに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:13.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめればよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:13.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなバカなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:12.83,default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have agreed\Nto this ridiculous challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:17.84,default,,0,0,0,,I don't want the money!\NI just want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.48,0:03:18.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金なんかいらない 俺は生きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:21.07,default,,0,0,0,,I want to live!\NI want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:22.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生きたい 生きたい 生きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:24.08,default,,0,0,0,,I want to live!\NI want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.92,0:03:26.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生きたい 生きたい！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:26.08,default,,0,0,0,,I want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.69,0:03:31.58,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa! Cut the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.69,0:03:32.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川！切れ 電流を！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.66,0:03:36.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金はいらない 中止だ 中止！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:36.19,default,,0,0,0,,We don't want the money!\NThe deal is off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.53,0:03:39.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいな？みんなもそれで！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.53,0:03:39.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:38.71,default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that?!\NEveryone, do you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:41.18,default,,0,0,0,,- Yes!\N- Switch it off! Switch it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:42.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,切って… 切って！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:42.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:42.33,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:44.12,default,,0,0,0,,Please switch it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:45.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,切ってください
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:45.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お願いします
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:45.33,default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:47.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お金はいりません
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.60,default,,0,0,0,,We don't need the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:50.97,default,,0,0,0,,We surrender! We quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:51.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まいりました 俺たち やめます
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:54.71,default,,0,0,0,,We give up! We give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:55.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギブアップ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:55.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギブアップー
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:01.21,default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.66,0:04:01.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お願いします
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:08.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ズレた命乞いだ ギブアップ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:07.72,default,,0,0,0,,Your pleas don't matter.\NGive up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.13,0:04:11.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真剣勝負にそんなものあるか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.13,0:04:11.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカどもが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:11.24,default,,0,0,0,,This is no time for backing out.\NYou've agreed and that's final.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:15.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,病気だな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:15.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,病気？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:12.99,default,,0,0,0,,They're sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:14.22,default,,0,0,0,,Sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:17.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんな事態に至ろうと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:20.26,default,,0,0,0,,It's a sickness that\Nblinds them from reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.51,0:04:21.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とことん真剣に
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.51,0:04:21.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なれない という病だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:26.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,命がけの勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:26.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敗北は死と伝えているのに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:23.07,default,,0,0,0,,They bet their lives on a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:28.05,default,,0,0,0,,Losing equals death. Yet they still\Nconsider the option of giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:28.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギブアップできると考える
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:31.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり真剣ではないのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:30.97,default,,0,0,0,,This means they are\Nnot serious at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.92,0:04:37.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この絶体絶命の橋ですら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.92,0:04:37.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真剣になれぬ ざれ言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:35.21,kaiji-main-top,,0,0,0,,Mr Tonegawa! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:36.71,default,,0,0,0,,They're standing on this\Nlife threatening bridge, yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:36.71,kaiji-main-top,,0,0,0,,Please turn off the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:41.15,default,,0,0,0,,They treat it\Nlike a virtual match.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:41.15,kaiji-main-top,,0,0,0,,Please! Please! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:41.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,架空の勝負 本当ではない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:47.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,通常 生涯ヤツらは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:47.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その空想から目覚めない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.72,0:04:45.82,default,,0,0,0,,They'll never wake up\Nfrom this virtual reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:50.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまらない毎日を送り
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:49.59,default,,0,0,0,,They live for the\Nsake of living...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:52.19,default,,0,0,0,,...just wasting\Ntheir time away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.17,0:04:53.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日々を無駄に塗りつぶし
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:56.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくつになろうと言い続けるのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:55.63,default,,0,0,0,,Despite getting older,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:04:59.78,default,,0,0,0,,they still think that their\Nreal lives have yet to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:05:01.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分の人生の本番は
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:05:01.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ先なんだと
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:06.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当の俺を使ってないから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:06.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今はこの程度なのだと
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:05.78,default,,0,0,0,,They think that\Nthey have yet to awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:11.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう言い続け… 言い続け…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:10.38,default,,0,0,0,,Those thoughts are\Nembedded in their minds...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:14.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,老いて 死ぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:14.22,default,,0,0,0,,...until they grow old and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:19.59,default,,0,0,0,,When the time comes,\Nthey will finally realise...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:20.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その間際 ようやく気づく
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:25.00,default,,0,0,0,,...that the lives they had\Nwas the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:24.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今まで生きてきたすべてが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:24.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,丸ごと本物だったことを
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:29.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人は仮になど生きていないし
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:31.20,default,,0,0,0,,Humans can neither\Nlive nor die virtually.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:31.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仮に死ぬこともできぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:34.64,default,,0,0,0,,It's a fact.\NBut the problem is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:34.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然だ 問題は…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.49,0:05:42.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その当然に
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.49,0:05:42.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気がついているかどうか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.64,0:05:42.48,default,,0,0,0,,...whether one realises it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:46.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真に覚醒しているかどうかだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:45.68,default,,0,0,0,,and whether one\Nbecomes aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:45.68,kaiji-main-top,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:49.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう考えれば この橋は荒療治だが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:49.64,default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,\Nthis bridge is the best way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:53.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツらが生まれ変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:53.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいきっかけかもしれん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:52.69,default,,0,0,0,,...to change them\Nfor the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:57.85,default,,0,0,0,,If they can pass\Nthis fatal phase,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:57.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この修羅… 死と相対した
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:57.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当の生を突破できれば
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:05:59.43,default,,0,0,0,,they may come to their senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:06:02.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目覚めるかも 頭の霧が晴れる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.02,0:06:01.93,default,,0,0,0,,They can think clearly then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:04.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,再生の扉が開く
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:04.53,default,,0,0,0,,And perhaps they'll change!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.86,0:06:15.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっとも… 突破できればだがな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.94,0:06:15.40,default,,0,0,0,,But, that's only if \N they can make it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:25.42,default,,0,0,0,,Nakayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:26.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:30.59,default,,0,0,0,,Nakayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:30.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中山！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:52.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うぎゃあー
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:54.74,default,,0,0,0,,Calm down! Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:56.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ち着け 石田さん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:58.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ち着け
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:06:57.80,default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:02.85,default,,0,0,0,,I'll fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:02.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お… 落ちる…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:05.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よせ やめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:03.82,default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:14.87,default,,0,0,0,,A chain reaction...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:18.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,連鎖 止まらない連鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:17.87,default,,0,0,0,,An unstoppable chain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.57,0:07:23.36,default,,0,0,0,,It's as if death is circling\NKaiji and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:23.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まるでカイジたちの上空を
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:23.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死に神が旋回していて
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:28.58,default,,0,0,0,,Starting from the weakest person,\Nhe'll kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.93,0:07:28.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心が弱った者の順に取りつき
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.93,0:07:28.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殺していくように
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:40.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カ… カイジ君…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:40.62,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:45.70,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:47.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君 助けて
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:47.63,default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.79,0:07:53.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うりゃあー！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:07.52,default,,0,0,0,,Minutes later when they finally\Nrealised, seven had fallen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:08.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気がつけば
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:08.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ものの２～３分で７人が落ち
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:12.46,default,,0,0,0,,...and three remained.\NKaiji, Ishida and Sahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:13.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残るはカイジ 石田 佐原の３人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:14.96,default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:15.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカか テメエら
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.35,0:08:18.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな橋の上で
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.35,0:08:18.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,支え合ったりなんかできねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:18.36,default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you can\Nhelp someone else on this bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:20.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自殺行為だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:19.89,default,,0,0,0,,It's suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:24.40,default,,0,0,0,,You can't save anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:24.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,助けられねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:24.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰も人を救えねえんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.78,0:08:25.96,default,,0,0,0,,You're on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.79,0:08:29.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人だ そばに誰がいようと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.79,0:08:29.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一切 関係ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:29.42,default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter\Nwho's beside you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:34.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,助かりたかったら
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:34.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自力で渡り切るしかねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:33.71,default,,0,0,0,,If you want to live,\Ncross the bridge yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.60,0:08:37.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それしかほかに道はねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:36.79,default,,0,0,0,,We have no other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:40.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違うか カイジ！石田！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.06,0:08:39.58,default,,0,0,0,,Am I right? Kaiji! Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.90,0:08:43.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は１人でも行く
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:43.59,default,,0,0,0,,I'm going alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:53.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ 佐原 お前は正しい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:52.06,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sahara. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:56.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行こう 石田さん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.58,0:08:55.20,default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:09:00.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちの気力が萎え
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:09:00.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,体力が本当に尽きてしまう前に
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.08,0:09:00.20,default,,0,0,0,,Before our energy lessens\Nand our bodies feel week.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:02.66,default,,0,0,0,,We will cross! Forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:03.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,渡るんだ 前へ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:06.61,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.59,0:09:07.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君 俺はダメ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:08.71,default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:09.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何言ってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:14.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はダメ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:15.35,default,,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:21.35,default,,0,0,0,,I can't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:21.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメなんだあ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:28.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっき落ちていった人間の
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:28.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残像が消えない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:27.99,default,,0,0,0,,I keep seeing images\Nof those who fell earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:31.36,default,,0,0,0,,My legs just\Nwon't stop shaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:31.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,足の震えが止まらないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:35.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,石田さん しっかりしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:35.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死にたいのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:35.35,default,,0,0,0,,Ishida! Hang on!\NDo you want to die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:37.42,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.86,0:09:38.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:43.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すまなかった 今までいろいろ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.90,0:09:40.77,default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:42.84,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:45.57,default,,0,0,0,,For saving me\Nback at the ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:45.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,船でも助けてもらって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:49.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今回もいろいろ励まして…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.88,0:09:49.76,default,,0,0,0,,...and encouraging me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.97,0:09:53.89,default,,0,0,0,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.01,0:09:58.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,石田さん 石田！落ち着け
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:55.89,default,,0,0,0,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:57.61,default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:10:02.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戻しを大きくするな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:10:02.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少しずつ戻せ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:10:00.16,default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:01.89,default,,0,0,0,,Move slowly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.32,0:10:03.70,default,,0,0,0,,Bit by bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.35,0:10:05.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少しずつ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:07.60,default,,0,0,0,,It's like the final\Ndance of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.99,0:10:12.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさに末期 死のダンス 断末魔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:09.73,default,,0,0,0,,Death throes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:15.74,default,,0,0,0,,The last dance for those\Non the brink of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:15.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死にゆく者の最後の舞だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:28.20,default,,0,0,0,,That's rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:30.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほう 珍しい 持ち直したぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:30.15,default,,0,0,0,,He recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:33.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが どうせあと１分か２分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:35.49,default,,0,0,0,,But it will only be for a\Nminute or two of his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.35,0:10:36.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,寿命が延びたにすぎん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:41.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいぞ 石田さん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:41.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫 行ける！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:37.66,default,,0,0,0,,Good, Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:40.08,default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NYou can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.63,0:10:43.42,default,,0,0,0,,K-Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:43.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カ… カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.48,0:11:04.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしたんだ？石田さん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.61,0:11:03.59,default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ishida?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:07.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのチケットは…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:06.19,default,,0,0,0,,That ticket...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:12.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君に託す
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:10.69,default,,0,0,0,,I'm entrusting\Nthis to you, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:15.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,虫のいい話なんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:15.37,default,,0,0,0,,It's the last favour\NI'm asking of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:19.02,default,,0,0,0,,I promise this\Nwill be the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.39,0:11:18.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の代わりに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.39,0:11:18.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このチケットを金に換え
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.93,0:11:20.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,渡してやってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:20.67,default,,0,0,0,,Help me exchange\N this for cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:24.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいことなんか 何にもなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:24.42,default,,0,0,0,,Then give it to\Nmy mother and my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:28.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,母ちゃん… 俺の連れ合い…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:28.01,default,,0,0,0,,I've disappointed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:33.50,default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:34.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい 何言ってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:37.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今も借金に追われて暮らしている
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:37.41,default,,0,0,0,,To this day, they're in\Ndebt because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.98,0:11:41.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな 俺のせいなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:40.76,default,,0,0,0,,Everything is my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:45.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,西京葉線 新富…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:45.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい 知らねえよ そんなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:43.22,default,,0,0,0,,Saikyouha Line Shintomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:45.36,default,,0,0,0,,Hey! That's not my problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.92,0:11:48.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな事情があるなら なおさら
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:48.26,default,,0,0,0,,That should be your motivation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.26,0:11:50.60,default,,0,0,0,,Cross over, and give it\Nto them yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.26,0:11:51.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,渡って 金を渡してやれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:53.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたが 自分で
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:53.49,default,,0,0,0,,Do it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:11:59.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君 分かったんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:58.97,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:01.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺にはもう分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:04.13,default,,0,0,0,,I know now that there are\Ntwo types of human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:04.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人間には２種類いる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:07.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,土壇場で臆して
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:07.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,動けなくなってしまう者と
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.44,0:12:07.92,default,,0,0,0,,Those who succumb to fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:11.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこで奮い立つ者と…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:10.30,default,,0,0,0,,and those who\Nstand up to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:14.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は そのダメなほう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:13.85,default,,0,0,0,,I belong to the first group.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:19.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう こうして立っているだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:19.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギリギリ… 精いっぱいなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:19.36,default,,0,0,0,,Standing here has\Ntaken a toil on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:22.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君は違う
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:21.80,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, you're different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:25.87,default,,0,0,0,,You're the kind\Nwho can make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:26.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君は できる人間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:31.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,困難に相対した時
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:31.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,めげずに立ち向かえる人間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.31,0:12:31.16,default,,0,0,0,,You can withstand any problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.40,0:12:33.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,芯の強い人間だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:33.87,default,,0,0,0,,You're very strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:36.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君ならできる… 託せる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:35.91,default,,0,0,0,,I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.91,0:12:37.18,default,,0,0,0,,So I can entrust you with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.31,0:12:45.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼む 西京葉線 新富下駅前の
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:43.55,default,,0,0,0,,Please, along\Nthe Saikyouha Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:47.89,default,,0,0,0,,...at the Shintomishita station,\Na Pachinko salon at Asahi Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.15,0:12:48.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アサヒホールというパチンコ屋で
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:55.43,kaiji-Sign-top,,0,0,0,,[Pachinko Asahi Hall]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:52.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安田という偽名で働いている
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:52.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,石田裕美に
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:52.98,default,,0,0,0,,Ishida Yumi, who goes by\Nthe alias of Yasuda works there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:56.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで得た金を渡してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:55.43,default,,0,0,0,,Please give her the money\Non my behalf...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:13:01.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで借金から解放…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:13:01.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救われるはずなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:13:01.17,default,,0,0,0,,With this, my debts will be\Ncleared and they'll be saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:04.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お願いだ カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:04.34,default,,0,0,0,,Please! Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:14.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,は… 早くっ 早く！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:14.22,default,,0,0,0,,Quick! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.42,0:13:24.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ 行ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.47,0:13:27.74,default,,0,0,0,,Hurry. Don't bother \Nabout me, just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.92,0:13:27.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺にかまわず 行ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:30.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,石田さん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:30.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:29.13,default,,0,0,0,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:30.63,default,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:46.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,振り返らないでくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:45.38,default,,0,0,0,,Don't look back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:50.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が落ちるのを見たら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:50.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君は動揺する
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:50.36,default,,0,0,0,,You'll be affected\Nif you see me fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.88,0:13:53.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな無駄なことを
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.88,0:13:53.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しちゃいけない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:53.38,default,,0,0,0,,Just keep your focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.88,0:13:58.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ前だけを見て進むんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:57.39,default,,0,0,0,,Look forward and move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.45,0:14:02.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てよ 勝て
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:14:02.01,default,,0,0,0,,Win... Win!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:04.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は敗れた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:04.39,default,,0,0,0,,I've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:11.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敗れて本当に無意味な…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:11.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無駄な一生だった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:10.40,default,,0,0,0,,I've lost and had\Na meaningless life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.13,0:14:15.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな一生を
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.13,0:14:15.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君は送っちゃいけない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.18,0:14:14.90,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, don't follow my path.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.40,0:14:20.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君は勝てる人間なんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:19.91,default,,0,0,0,,You're someone who\Ncan succeed, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:25.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ってくれ 勝つんだ カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:25.15,default,,0,0,0,,Win... Win, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.98,0:14:31.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敗れて本当に無意味な…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:31.65,default,,0,0,0,,I've lost, and had\Na meaningless life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:34.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違う 無意味なんかじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.65,0:14:34.66,default,,0,0,0,,No! It wasn't meaningless!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:38.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,石田さんは祈れたじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.01,0:14:37.87,default,,0,0,0,,Ishida, you prayed, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:42.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最期の時に自分以外の人間を
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.88,0:14:45.41,default,,0,0,0,,At the last moment,\Nyou thought of others!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:45.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心から案ずることのできた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:45.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,石田さんは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:49.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんなに人間として上等か
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:48.67,default,,0,0,0,,Ishida, you're a good man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.34,0:14:52.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう やり遂げたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:54.91,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you did it.\NIshida, you did great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:55.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,石田さんは立派に達した
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:15:00.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けなんかじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:15:00.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,むしろ立派に勝った
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:14:59.68,default,,0,0,0,,You didn't lose.\NYou won a great victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.28,0:15:02.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,石田さん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:01.54,default,,0,0,0,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.71,0:15:31.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ちた 落ちちまった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.75,0:15:30.94,default,,0,0,0,,He fell... He fell down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.31,0:15:34.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無言で落ちた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:33.04,default,,0,0,0,,He fell without a sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:38.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,怖がりで臆病者の石田さんが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:38.17,default,,0,0,0,,A timid person like Ishida...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:41.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺に動揺を与えないために
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:41.42,default,,0,0,0,,...fell in silence\Nso as not to affect me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:49.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黙って落ちた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:49.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悲鳴のひとかけらも発さず
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:46.89,default,,0,0,0,,He fell in silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:49.20,default,,0,0,0,,He sacrificed himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.96,0:15:52.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶叫を強引にねじ伏せた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:53.70,default,,0,0,0,,He endured,\Nwhile muffling his screams!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:57.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,耐えた 耐え抜いた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:55.58,default,,0,0,0,,He endured it till the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:16:00.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,石田さんは示した
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:16:02.14,default,,0,0,0,,Ishida, right to the very end...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:07.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後の最後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:07.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,石田さんの意地 強さ 矜持を
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.43,0:16:07.21,default,,0,0,0,,His willpower,\Nstrength and pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.44,0:16:28.51,default,,0,0,0,,I'll make it!\NI'll definitely cross!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:30.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,渡る 絶対に渡る やり遂げる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:30.47,default,,0,0,0,,I will finish this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:35.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仮に死ぬことになっても強く死ぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.97,0:16:34.82,default,,0,0,0,,Even if I die,\NI'll die with pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.31,0:16:38.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,石田さんのように死ぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:37.16,default,,0,0,0,,Die, just like Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:40.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目の前の一歩がすべて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:40.00,default,,0,0,0,,Each step is precious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:45.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この小さな一歩を
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:45.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただただ積み重ねていけばいい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.61,0:16:42.32,default,,0,0,0,,I need to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:44.76,default,,0,0,0,,I need to keep moving forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:48.99,default,,0,0,0,,One step at a time!\NOne step!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:48.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一歩ずつ 一歩ずつ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:54.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそっ 立っていやがる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:53.49,default,,0,0,0,,Darn! He stood up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.37,0:16:55.74,default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Sahara?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.39,0:16:58.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした 佐原？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.39,0:16:58.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,太田の野郎が…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:57.74,default,,0,0,0,,That guy, Oota...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.89,0:16:58.80,default,,0,0,0,,Oota?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:17:01.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,太田？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:17:01.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,テメエ いい加減にしろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:01.33,default,,0,0,0,,Darn it... Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:04.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は確かに
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:04.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前を救わなかったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:04.34,default,,0,0,0,,I know I didn't save you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.53,0:17:06.57,default,,0,0,0,,...and I didn't try to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:06.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手を差し伸べなかったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:09.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恨むのはお門違いってもんだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:09.36,default,,0,0,0,,But you have\Nno right to hate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:11.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを今さら…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:11.37,default,,0,0,0,,Nor to do this now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:16.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よせ 佐原 口なんかきくな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:16.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは幻だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:12.85,default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Sahara!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.85,0:17:15.81,default,,0,0,0,,Ignore it!\NIt's just an illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.35,0:17:21.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前へ 踏みこらえろ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.35,0:17:21.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が行けば亡霊のほうで下がる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.58,0:17:18.31,default,,0,0,0,,Forward! Step forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:21.32,default,,0,0,0,,If you move, it'll go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:29.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ 攻めろ 攻めるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:28.79,default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Attack! Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:31.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここが正念場だぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:30.79,default,,0,0,0,,This is your crucial moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.01,0:17:46.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,佐原？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:45.10,default,,0,0,0,,Sahara?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:48.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,消えた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:47.54,default,,0,0,0,,He disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.55,0:17:51.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほど ここは現実なんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:51.74,default,,0,0,0,,I see.\NIn reality, the living...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:56.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死んだ者より
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:56.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生きてる俺の気持ちが優先される
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.74,0:17:55.42,default,,0,0,0,,...matter more than the dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:18:00.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ 渡るぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:18:00.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,渡りさえすれば金… ２０００万！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:57.75,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.75,0:18:00.42,default,,0,0,0,,We're getting 20 million\Nif we make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.63,0:18:05.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,邪魔するヤツは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.63,0:18:05.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たとえ亡霊でも突き落とす
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:04.29,default,,0,0,0,,Just get rid of\Nanyone who obstructs us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:07.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,佐原
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.22,0:18:06.67,default,,0,0,0,,Sahara...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.34,0:18:18.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと６メートル
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:18.24,default,,0,0,0,,Six metres to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:21.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無情に吹き始めた突風
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:20.81,default,,0,0,0,,A sudden gust of\Nwind starts howling!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.82,0:18:24.58,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji and Sahara\Nendure it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.82,0:18:25.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,懸命に耐えるカイジと佐原
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:27.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそっ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.32,0:18:26.08,default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:33.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,思い返せば 何という孤独なレース
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.26,0:18:32.70,default,,0,0,0,,To think about it,\Nthis is a lonely race.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:35.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,周りに何人いようが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:37.74,default,,0,0,0,,You can't support\Nanyone around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:38.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決して支え合ったりできない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:44.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし よくよく考えれば
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:44.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それはこの橋に限らない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.83,0:18:44.08,default,,0,0,0,,Then again, \Nit doesn't only apply here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.94,0:18:51.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつだって人は…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.94,0:18:51.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その心は孤立している
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:46.60,default,,0,0,0,,A person's heart is\Nalways isolated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:50.60,default,,0,0,0,,No one can\N understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:56.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心は誰にも理解されない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:56.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,伝わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.21,0:18:55.84,default,,0,0,0,,And no one can make\Npeople understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.02,0:18:59.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 誰もが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.02,0:18:59.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,理解と愛情を求めて…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:18:59.58,default,,0,0,0,,That's why everyone yearns\Nfor empathy and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:04.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,求めて… 求め続けているが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:03.47,default,,0,0,0,,They seek it,\Nagain and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:08.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局 近づけない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:07.29,default,,0,0,0,,But they never grow closer\Nas a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:12.73,default,,0,0,0,,6.6 billion inhabitants\Nof this world walk alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:13.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,孤独な１本道を行く
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:13.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世界の６６億の民
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:19.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,天空を行く１人１人… ６６億の孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:18.23,default,,0,0,0,,Everyone walking the skyway\Ncreate 6.6 billion lonely paths.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:22.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手は届かない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:22.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はるか遠く離れている
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:22.48,default,,0,0,0,,They can't reach for each other.\NEveryone is too far apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.84,0:19:25.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できることは通信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:25.24,default,,0,0,0,,You can only communicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.75,0:19:28.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ 大丈夫か カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:28.94,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!\NAre you okay, Kaiji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:35.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ 大丈夫だ 佐原
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.99,0:19:34.95,default,,0,0,0,,Yes!\NI'm okay, Sahara!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:38.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それはあまりに か細く
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.81,0:19:38.36,default,,0,0,0,,Although the\Ncommunication is weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.33,0:19:41.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真の理解とは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.33,0:19:41.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほど遠いかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:41.19,default,,0,0,0,,...and difficult to comprehend,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.63,0:19:44.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 生きている者の息づかいは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.69,0:19:44.76,default,,0,0,0,,But the communication\Nbetween the living,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:48.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わずかに だが確かに伝わる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:48.44,default,,0,0,0,,however weak,\Nstill goes through.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:51.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:51.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,佐原！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.74,0:19:50.34,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:51.20,default,,0,0,0,,Sahara!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:54.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いるか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:54.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここにいるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:52.81,default,,0,0,0,,Are you still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:54.20,default,,0,0,0,,I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.87,0:19:58.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は佐原を救えない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:57.78,default,,0,0,0,,I can't save Sahara...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.65,0:20:00.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:20:00.18,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.61,0:20:04.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いる いるぞ 佐原 いる！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:03.22,default,,0,0,0,,I'm here!\NI'm here, Sahara!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:04.21,default,,0,0,0,,Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.15,0:20:08.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶望的に離ればなれだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:08.21,default,,0,0,0,,Both of us are\Nhopelessly separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.96,0:20:13.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なのに 何だ このぬくもりは
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:12.15,default,,0,0,0,,But... I feel comforted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:19.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,胸から湧いてくる温かさ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:19.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,感謝の気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.61,0:20:16.00,default,,0,0,0,,The warmth\Nspreads through my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:18.02,default,,0,0,0,,This feeling of gratitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.37,0:20:23.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,佐原が ただそこにいるだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.37,0:20:23.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救われる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:23.19,default,,0,0,0,,Sahara's presence alone\Ngives me a sense of security.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.11,0:20:30.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか そういうことか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:29.00,default,,0,0,0,,I see. That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:35.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人間が…
